oto albums. The game combines handcrafted atmosphere with real historical footage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133340/extras/VLV89_CZ_heading04.png?t=1730723076\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">takes place in four cities and at five protests that made the Velvet Revolution happen </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">features a hidden-object gameplay with more than 40 stories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">uses stylized visuals that combine handcrafted graphics and actual historical footage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">was made with experts and is based on real testimonies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The game was developed in cooperation with educational programme One World in Schools to commemorate the 35th anniversary of the Velvet Revolution. It was created as a part of the Stories of Injustice project, which aims to introduce our country\u2019s modern history to young people.</i></p>","developers":["Charles Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133340/header.jpg?t=1730723076","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257041626,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041626/movie480.mp4?t=1723535907","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041626/movie_max.mp4?t=1723535907"},"name":"Velvet 89 Teaser","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257041626/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1723535907","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041626/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1723535907","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2